<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <title>Happy Birthday!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        margin: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        overflow: scroll;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        width: 40%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
      .floating {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        animation: float 3s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
      }
      .balloons {
        font-size: 4rem;
      }
      .cloud {
        background: white;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        width: 300px;
        height: 150px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #ff4081;
        box-shadow: 5px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }
      .cloud::before,
      .cloud::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 50%;
      }
      .cloud::before {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        top: -50px;
        left: 10px;
      }
      .cloud::after {
        width: 90px;
        height: 90px;
        top: -30px;
        right: 10px;
      }
      .card1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        height: 35rem;
        color: black;
      }
      @keyframes float {
        from {
          transform: translateY(0px);
        }
        to {
          transform: translateY(1.5rem);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="floating">
        <div class="cloud mt-2">Timeless Wonder 💎</div>
        <div class="balloons">🎈🎂💕</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card1">
        I want to share something with you. As you know, I was never truly happy
        in my previous college, but the day you texted me for the first time,
        everything changed 💫. <br /><br />I still feel grateful to SD College
        for bringing us together 🤝, but I deeply regret not giving you the
        attention you deserved when we first met 😞. <br /><br />
        I used to be camera-shy 😅, but you always encouraged me to send photos
        of myself 📸, and that helped me overcome my fear of being in front of
        the camera 🙌😊.
        <br /><br />
        I know that due to some misunderstandings, we’re not as close now, but I
        truly hope you always stay happy and healthy. 😊💖 All these things I
        just mentioned became true because of you 💫.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
